edu.cnm.deepdive.celestialbodies.units

Class Matrix33

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.celestialbodies.units.Matrix33
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public class Matrix33
extends Object
implements Cloneable
    Class for representing a 3x3 matrix explicitly, avoiding heap allocation as far as possible. This class is made use of by the Celestial Bodies app.
    Author:
    Dominic Widdows
